<head>
  
</head>

<div class="homepage-content">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <%= image_tag 'marketplace_logo.png', alt: 'Marketplace Logo', class: 'homepage-logo' %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="top-sellers">
      <h2>Top Sellers</h2>
      <% @top_sellers.each do |seller| %>
        <div class="seller">
          <%= link_to seller.username, user_path(seller), class: "seller-link" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </section>

    <section class="featured-products">
      <h2>Featured Products</h2>
      <% @featured_products.each do |product| %>
        <div class="product">
          <%= link_to product_path(product) do %>
            <h3><%= product.title %></h3>
            <%= image_tag(product.image) if product.image.attached? %>
            <p><%= number_to_currency(product.price) %></p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </section>
    <section class="top-sellers">
      <h2>Top Rated Sellers</h2>
      <% @top_rated.each do |seller|%>
        <div class="seller">
          <%= link_to seller.username, user_path(seller), class: "seller-link"%>
          <%= number_with_precision(seller.average_rating, precision:1) %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </section>
  </main>
  <div>
  <section class="about-us">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Knockoff eBay is your go-to place for buying and selling a wide variety of products. We offer a secure and easy-to-use platform for both buyers and sellers.</p>
    <br/>
    <br/>
  </section>
  </div>
  <div>
    <section class="about-us">
      <h2>FAQ</h2>
      <br/>
      <h3>How do I sign up?</h3>
      <p>Click the sign up button in the top right of your screen. You can authenticate through our website or sign in through GitHub!</p>
      <br/>
      <h3>How do I find the kind of products I am looking for?</h3>
      <p>Buyers can search by a variety of different categories, through text search, by price range and more.</p>
      <br/>
      <h3>Can I save a product listing and come back to it later?</h3>
      <p>Yes! When viewing a product click "Add to Favorites" to save the product for viewing later. You can then access the listing later by hitting the heart icon in the navigation bar.</p>
      <br/>
      <h3>How can I report an issue?</h3>
      <p>If you have an issue with another member you can report them from their profile page, allowing you to speak with an admin and get it resolved!</p>
      <br/>
      <h3>What if I have more questions about a product that aren't listed in the description?</h3>
      <p>If you have questions about a product feel free to use our messaging feature! This will allow you to connect with the seller and ask any questions you might have.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
  <br/>
  <br/>
  <footer>
    <p> 2023 Knockoff eBay. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</div>

